MERN stack is a framework that is used for full stack web development. Each letter in the word MERN stands for MongoDB, Express, React, Node which makes us eligible for being a full stack web developer. 

INSTALLING IDE:
BROWSER--> Installing Node.js (Move forward with the LTS version)

After installing the IDE :
Open terminal .
Type node --v (checks the installed version)
Next, npm -v(tells us the npm version installed)

Download the Visual Studio.
